Interface MaskedPassword

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Destroyable, Key, Password, Serializable, TwoWayPassword

    public interface MaskedPassword
extends TwoWayPassword
    A password which has been masked, PicketBox style.
    Author:
    David M. Lloyd
